{"id": 1557, "genre": 1001, "title": "影视剧都给过你什么样的生活灵感？", "description": "虽然对硬性植入的纯净水、牛奶广告不屑一顾，但还是不经意被花式种草。（题图来自：Antti Kalevi）", "record_count": 3249, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170307170117RDnpTkOcgtyIszGe.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-03-09T03:00:25Z", "options": [{"id": 183552, "content": "看了国产剧就会不断买同款吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 981691}, {"id": 177410, "content": "呵呵\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 965517}, {"id": 176899, "content": "武藏牌牛奶唤起了我喝牛奶的激情", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 553535}, {"id": 176900, "content": "看了鬼怪后想把新家装成那样", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 865269}, {"id": 177156, "content": "看了犯罪心理想去当执法人员啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 964604}, {"id": 177412, "content": "看灵魂摆渡五胡乱华那集后不吃烤串了", "image": "img/option/option/20170310173735e65fghcGu2iOqFmW", "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 907223}, {"id": 177157, "content": "还记得刘亦菲版神雕侠侣热播的那一段时间，中央一台一直在播那种文化宣传片，还记得里面一开始是优美的英语女声歌曲，画面出现风车，一群跳舞的可爱的外国小孩，教堂里蓝眸金发女孩撩开窗帘，对着明媚的阳光向往地微笑，画面突转，绿茵中，出现碧绿色的湖水，翠绿色的竹林，一位穿旗袍的，温润清丽的中", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 859962}, {"id": 176902, "content": "我想做一个独立自主的BITCH。观《girls》后感", "image": null, "praise_count": 65, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 963884}, {"id": 177158, "content": "各种剧的女主妆", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 807486}, {"id": 177159, "content": "表示没有", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 957080}, {"id": 176904, "content": "看完神夏后果断买了长款风衣➕衬衫", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 937690}, {"id": 177160, "content": "国女孩乘舟吹笛，好一朵美丽的茉莉花，。接下来的我不太记得，但是却是启迪了我心中对文化交融，无国界的理解。我开始对世界文化无名地崇敬，这就是传播的力量，它在这墨色的大地上发光发亮，化做一股清流，打破时间，滋润着枯黄的思想，冲击着封闭心灵的万里长城。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 859962}, {"id": 177161, "content": "独宠乡村爱情，温暖的生活，给人安慰", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 321906}, {"id": 252681, "content": "看完小埋，学会了薯片+可乐", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1203674}, {"id": 176906, "content": "看完龙珠总觉得自己也能变成赛亚人", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 808042}, {"id": 206603, "content": "看完欢乐颂感觉作为一个女生 以后还是奋斗出自给自足的程度比较好 追求纯粹的爱情 男人不是巨大的依靠 每个人都是独立体", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1038173}, {"id": 177163, "content": "看完夏洛克，突然想做基佬", "image": "img/option/option/20170309222527MPOaFqRy7nzYfet4", "praise_count": 41, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 214616}, {"id": 194571, "content": "看着里面演员吃的东西，都禁不住地咽口水", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 492903}, {"id": 204300, "content": "看大长今之后，吃饭都摆一碗汤在旁边。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 595170}, {"id": 176908, "content": "《大西洋帝国》《纸牌屋》《教父》都是爱到不行，作为信仰", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 951433}, {"id": 176909, "content": "总感觉日剧跑很青春", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 963890}, {"id": 177421, "content": "中二是种病", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 962109}, {"id": 178189, "content": "嗯。棒棒哒", "image": "img/option/option/201703131055365GipB8bIThw3S0Yu.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 965181}, {"id": 176910, "content": "看美食类韩剧「一起用餐吧」硬生生学会做n种韩国料理，韩国海鲜粥什么的信手拈来", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 416515}, {"id": 177166, "content": "《广告狂人》，乙方也可以很牛", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 929754}, {"id": 177422, "content": "多久时间快说快说开裆裤打卡可大可大可大可大卡卡都可大可大哦对啦对咯都可哦饿哦饿哦饿哦", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 965630}, {"id": 176911, "content": "啤酒加炸鸡", "image": null, "praise_count": 227, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 956251}, {"id": 177168, "content": "法医成为心头肉", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 915546}, {"id": 184080, "content": "看完垫底辣妹突然很想看书学习", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 983309}, {"id": 177169, "content": "看完哈利波特买了根魔杖\n觉得自己有魔法", "image": "img/option/option/20170309223924YHKjyiLc0s4CW6BR", "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 964581}, {"id": 177425, "content": "十二岁看完流星雨，觉得美特斯邦威很时尚", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 965642}, {"id": 176914, "content": "看了《绝命毒师》后，我开始学习....", "image": null, "praise_count": 180, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 963911}, {"id": 177426, "content": "看了咏春想去练武吊打一切", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 956420}, {"id": 176915, "content": "看完<吹响!上低音号>想去了解交响乐", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 913230}, {"id": 176916, "content": "电动牙刷", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 407163}, {"id": 177172, "content": "hi", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 964673}, {"id": 177428, "content": "不知道说什么 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 965657}, {"id": 176917, "content": "看完爆裂鼓手想学架子鼓！", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 951571}, {"id": 177429, "content": "看了灵魂摆渡五胡乱华那部突然想起了冉闵", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 931256}, {"id": 177174, "content": "看了 《行尸走肉》想学化妆", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 949136}, {"id": 177430, "content": "冉闵和广告没有关系", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 931256}, {"id": 176919, "content": "会吃着日料看日剧", "image": "img/option/option/20170309115510SKCT94g2dYW5mEbN.jpg", "praise_count": 33, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 533504}, {"id": 177175, "content": "看了《黑执事》之后买了一套国际象棋", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 262001}, {"id": 176920, "content": "看完日剧开始写planner！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 234967}, {"id": 177177, "content": "看了轻音少女之后开始学吉他。。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 964687}, {"id": 206874, "content": "看了欢乐颂之后就发现自己男朋友咋就这么差劲呢，没有包奕凡有趣，没有王柏川痴情，没有赵医生有内涵，越看越不顺眼", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1039157}, {"id": 176922, "content": "中二来源？", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 416374}, {"id": 177180, "content": "看了《纸牌屋》再也不想当美国总统了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 960817}, {"id": 195612, "content": "曼妥思放入可乐里", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1012556}, {"id": 176925, "content": "看完韩剧立刻买了一套女主同款", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 920921}]}